  : ùíØ (Œª x a => f a x) = Œª x dx => ‚ü®Œª a => f a x, Œª a => ‚àÇ (f a) x dx, rfl‚ü©
  := by simp[tangentMapDep']; done

@[simp ‚Üì low-1, autodiff low-1]
